trans-unit.source: Manages anonymous identifiers for the ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Administrerer anonym identifikatorer for ASP.NET-programmet.

trans-unit.source: The AnonymousIdentificationModule class creates and manages anonymous identifiers for an ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AnonymousIdentificationModule oppretter og administrerer anonym identifikatorer for en ASP.NET-programmet.

trans-unit.source: Anonymous identifiers are used by features that support anonymous identification such as the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Profile>.
trans-unit.target: Anonym identifikatorer som brukes av funksjoner som støtter anonym identifisering som ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Profile>.</xref:System.Web.Profile>

trans-unit.source: The AnonymousIdentificationModule exposes a <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event that enables you to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value.
trans-unit.target: AnonymousIdentificationModule viser en <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>hendelse som lar deg angi anonym ID til en egendefinert verdi.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a custom anonymous identifier value, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en egendefinert anonym ID-verdi, en <xref:System.Guid>brukes.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event is accessed by specifying a subroutine named **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>hendelsen brukes ved å angi en underrutine navnet **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** i filen Global.asax for ASP.NET-program.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>

trans-unit.source: The AnonymousIdentificationModule is only used when anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A> by setting the enabled attribute of the configuration element to `true`.
trans-unit.target: AnonymousIdentificationModule brukes bare når anonym identifisering <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>ved å angi attributtet enabled for konfigurasjonselementet til `true`.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Anonymous identification is independent of any type of ASP.NET authentication.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Anonym identifisering er uavhengig av en annen type for ASP.NET-godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is not intended to be called from application code.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren skal ikke kalles fra programmet kode.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET calls this constructor to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> class.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET kaller denne konstruktøren for å opprette en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>klassen.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>

trans-unit.source: After calling the constructor, it calls the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Init%2A> method to initialize the new <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> object.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall til konstruktøren, kaller den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Init%2A>metode for å initialisere den nye <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>objektet.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Init%2A>

trans-unit.source: Clears the anonymous cookie or identifier associated with a session.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner anonym informasjonskapsel eller identifikator tilknyttet en økt.

trans-unit.source: The ClearAnonymousIdentifier method removes the anonymous identifier associated with a session on a Web site.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ClearAnonymousIdentifier fjerner anonym ID knyttet til økten på et webområde.

trans-unit.source: Use the ClearAnonymousIdentifier method to remove the anonymous identifier associated with a session when the user switches to an authenticated session associated with a user ID, for example when the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.MigrateAnonymous> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Bruk ClearAnonymousIdentifier for å fjerne anonym ID som er forbundet med en økt når brukeren bytter til en godkjent økt som er knyttet til en bruker-IDen, for eksempel når den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.MigrateAnonymous>inntreffer.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.MigrateAnonymous>

trans-unit.source: Since a new anonymous identifier will be issued immediately if the current anonymous identifier is removed, the ClearAnonymousIdentifier method will throw a <xref:System.NotSupportedException> if it is called while the session is identified by an anonymous identifier.
trans-unit.target: Etter en ny anonym ID får umiddelbart hvis den gjeldende anonyme-IDen er fjernet, metoden ClearAnonymousIdentifier vil throw en <xref:System.NotSupportedException>Hvis kalles mens økten er identifisert av en anonym ID.</xref:System.NotSupportedException>

trans-unit.source: If the site is using cookies, the ClearAnonymousIdentifier method issues a clear cookie to remove the anonymous identifier from the browser.
trans-unit.target: Hvis området bruker informasjonskapsler, utstedes metoden ClearAnonymousIdentifier en Fjern informasjonskapsel (cookie) Hvis du vil fjerne anonym ID fra nettleseren.

trans-unit.source: The clear cookie is issued even if an anonymous cookie was not sent on the previous request.
trans-unit.target: Fjern informasjonskapselen utstedes selv om en anonym ikke ble sendt på forrige forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: The clear cookie is constructed as follows: - If the browser supports empty strings in a cookie, the cookie is issued with the empty string as its value; otherwise, the cookie is issued with "NoCookie" as its value.
trans-unit.target: Fjern informasjonskapselen ser slik ut:-om nettleseren støtter tomme strenger i en informasjonskapsel, informasjonskapselen utstedes med en tom streng som verdien. informasjonskapselen ellers brukes sammen med "NoCookie" som verdi.

trans-unit.source: - The values for the cookie name, path, and domain are set to the defaults configured in the Web application's configuration file.
trans-unit.target: -Verdier for informasjonskapselnavn, bane og domenet er angitt til standardverdiene konfigurert i konfigurasjonsfilen for Web-applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: - The expiration date is set to October 12, 1999.
trans-unit.target: -Utløpsdatoen er satt til 12 oktober 1999.

trans-unit.source: If the site is using cookieless authentication, and an anonymous identifier is present in the URL, the anonymous identifier is removed from the URL.
trans-unit.target: Hvis området bruker uten informasjonskapsel godkjenning, og en anonym ID mangler i URL-adressen, fjernes den anonyme-IDen fra URL-adressen.

trans-unit.source: No other changes are made to the address or query string.
trans-unit.target: Ingen andre endringer til streng for postadressen eller spørringen.

trans-unit.source: After the URL is modified, a redirect is issued to return to the currently executing page.
trans-unit.target: Når URL-adressen er endret, sendes en omadressering for å gå tilbake til siden for øyeblikket kjøres.

trans-unit.source: Calling ClearAnonymousIdentifier when the anonymous identification is not enabled.
trans-unit.target: Kaller ClearAnonymousIdentifier når anonym identifisering ikke er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: -or- The user for the current request is anonymous.
trans-unit.target: - eller - brukeren for gjeldende forespørsel er anonym.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when a new anonymous identifier is created.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når en ny anonym ID er opprettet.

trans-unit.source: The Creating event is raised during the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.PostAuthenticateRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: Opprette hendelsen oppstår under den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.PostAuthenticateRequest>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.PostAuthenticateRequest>

trans-unit.source: You can access the Creating event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> class by specifying a subroutine named **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til hendelsen opprette for den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>klassen ved å angi en underrutine navnet **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** i filen Global.asax for ASP.NET-program.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object supplied to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs>objektet som er angitt for den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** -hendelsen for å angi anonym ID til en egendefinert verdi.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en verdi for den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>egenskapen under den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** hendelsen en <xref:System.Guid>brukes.</xref:System.Guid> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event is only raised when the anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** denne hendelsen oppstår bare når anonym identifisering er <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>
